title: Mr. Wong The Fatal Hour (1940) BORIS KARLOFF

sources.title: Mr. Wong The Fatal Hour (1940) BORIS KARLOFF
sources.description:
Stars: Boris Karloff, Marjorie Reynolds, Grant Withers
Director: William Nigh

When Captain Street's best friend is murdered, He enlists the help of detective James Lee Wong. Mr. Wong uncovers a smuggling ring on the waterfront of San Francisco and unmasks the killer, though not until several more murders occur!
